OL,3,CManslaughter charge after death of
OL,4,CCarl Holland
OL,6,FA man has been charged with
OL,7,Fmanslaughter by detectives
OL,8,Finvestigating the death of Carl
OL,9,FHolland.
OL,11,FThe 30-year-old died on Friday, a week
OL,12,Fafter an assault outside a pub in the
OL,13,FSuffolk Road area of west Belfast on
OL,14,Fthe night of June 12.
OL,16,FHe was in a critical condition and was
OL,17,Freceiving treatment to a serious head
OL,18,Finjury.
OL,20,FPolice said Mr Holland was from the
OL,21,Farea.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
