OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1782127153
OL,3,CManslaughter charge after death of
OL,4,CCarl Holland
OL,6,FA 20-year-old man is due to appear
OL,7,Fbefore Belfast Magistrates' Court on
OL,8,FWednesday.
OL,10,FIn a statement, the PSNI said: "As is
OL,11,Fusual procedure, the charge will be
OL,12,Freviewed by the Public Prosecution
OL,13,FService."
OL,15,FA 46-year-old man and a 44-year-old
OL,16,Fwoman who were arrested on suspicion
OL,17,Fof conspiracy to commit grievous
OL,18,Fbodily harm have subsequently been
OL,19,Freleased on bail to allow for further
OL,20,Fenquiries.
